WEBVTT

00:01.169 --> 00:02.449
All right. It's Christmas night.

00:04.105 --> 00:05.315
Spike that egg nog
and grab the wife,

00:05.339 --> 00:06.607
'cause there's trouble brewin'.

00:08.000 --> 00:14.074
